reviews.text:
Very friendly staffs!

The soup was great 👍🏻 like homemade by mom. (Don’t tell it to my mom 🤪)

Hainam Chicken Rice (set) was the last thing you would want to miss.

Although it’s not their best dish, the Tom Yum Kung Fried Rice was something exciting that you would not expect in an ordinary Cha Chaan Teng menu.
待應友善。餸菜，湯...好味。㕑師用心煮。如果魚的種類多D，蒸魚時間再合適D就更好。
早餐唔錯，快靚正
午餐平靚正，早餐一般，晚飯未試過。
待應主動幫手追單, 不錯的服務態度
